### Summary

| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **Routes** | Fastify plugins in `/modules/{feature}/{feature}.routes.ts` with Zod schemas |
| **Services** | Optional service files for complex logic (e.g., telegram-auth.service.ts) |
